Program: Outlook
Title: Shiran Ebadi
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbs35
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
An interview with Shiran Ebadi, the Iranian 2003 Nobel Peace Prize winner. Also, the HIV positive woman in Kiev campaigning against Aids across Eastern Europe. Survivors of the Java earthquake on losing everything. A documentary about the child survivors of the 2007 earthquake in Pakistan. Controversy over television for babies in the US. Finally Hind Al-Hinnawi and her legal battle to have her daughter's identity recognised. Show less